Title: Steadfast (The Lost Fleet: Beyond the Frontier, #4)
Author: Jack Campbell
My Review:
The story continues... A good read that was quite enjoyable. I keep finding myself waiting again for the next episode of this great scifi series, only it's months rather than days between books!

Let's be honest, if you are already this far into the series you've enjoyed something about the last books and this is more of the same.

If you haven't read any of them, the author does write to keep things accessible to people just dropping into the story, but go back and read from the beginning.

And of course, a twist in the end keeps you hooked for the next book... I won't spoil it.

...
In compliance with FTC guidelines, I disclose in my review that I received the book for free through Goodreads First Reads.
